<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="303" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="10.[138,777,762,882]" pageId="10" pageNumber="303">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[138,264,762,787]" pageId="10" pageNumber="303">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[138,242,763,787]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="303">Remarks.</emphasis>
–
</emphasis>
This species was reported as a new record for 
<collectingCountry box="[138,202,795,818]" name="China" pageId="10" pageNumber="303">China</collectingCountry>
from 
<collectingRegion box="[268,494,795,818]" country="China" name="Guangdong" pageId="10" pageNumber="303">Guangdong Province</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Pilato, G" box="[509,644,795,818]" pageId="10" pageNumber="303" pagination="59 - 68" refId="ref4594" refString="Pilato, G., 1974. Tre nuove specie di Tardigradi muscicoli di Cina. Animalia, 1: 59 - 68." type="journal article" year="1974">Pilato, 1974</bibRefCitation>
). It was also reported from 
<collectingRegion box="[293,480,827,850]" country="China" name="Yunnan" pageId="10" pageNumber="303">Yunnan Province</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Beasley, C" box="[494,711,827,850]" pageId="10" pageNumber="303" pagination="3 - 10" refId="ref4286" refString="Beasley, C. W., L. Kaczmarek &amp; L. Michalczyk, 2006. New records of tardigrades from China, with zoogeographical remarks. Biological Letter, 43: 3 - 10." type="journal article" year="2006">Beasley et al., 2006</bibRefCitation>
). This is the first report of this species from 
<collectingRegion box="[547,624,859,882]" country="China" name="Hainan" pageId="10" pageNumber="303">Hainan</collectingRegion>
Island.
</paragraph>
